Take map folder and put inside of 
Steamapps/ username/ counterstrike source/ cstrike
Put sound cache in 
Steamapps/ username/ counterstrike source/ cstrike/ maps
There are many folders i realised just keep clicking through them sorry about that

The map is of a large city that has been taken over by the terrorists the power is almost completley out you have limited time before the terrorists come and turn out the power completley SAVE THE CITY!

The city has been overran by terorrist forces 
Terrorist: your job is to sucessfully bomb the last thing in the city to destroy the city the oil drum and their technology is next to the oil drum do whatever means necessary

Counter terrorist: your job is to stop the terrorist's from sucessfully bombing the oil drum and the tech do whatever means necessary

This could be very laggy on your pc so i suggest you turn down your graphics
